{"tid":1513183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廉署控警員涉訛稱母醫病騙同袍8.3萬元","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:38:34.000Z","uid":58307,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc5613946cac3fb49e9279601eeaa18c80c1354","tid":1513183,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"一名高級警員涉嫌以欺詐手段向多名同袍騙取逾8.3萬元貸款，被廉政公署落案起訴，被告獲廉署批准保釋，星期五在西九龍裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指出，49歲被告林仲文，案發時在深水埗分區一個巡邏小隊任職高級警員，涉嫌2018年先後10次，不誠實地向6名同袍訛稱需要金錢，支付母親在內地的醫療費用，意圖詐騙誘使他們提供10筆貸款，介乎約6000元至2.5萬元。"},{"pid":"2f1c54300719b32beb30659680d6b3122e2946e4","tid":1513183,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5M%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=22b50158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5M%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=4bb554f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5M%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=bcb5b931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"3052d5709f70d71225d0b257e5b9b7c13122ba8e","tid":1513183,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"